title: The WeBurnout Edition
description:
Millennial burnout, odd rebranding efforts, and the World Bank. with Felix Salmon, Anna Szymanski, and Emily Peck.
In the Slate Plus segment, Emily, Anna, and Felix discuss government workers pay during the shutdown.
